ConformanceStatementStatus

The status of this conformance statement

This value set defines its own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/conformance-statement-status

CodeDisplayDefinition
draftThis conformance statement is still under development.
activeThis conformance statement is ready for use in production systems.
retiredThis conformance statement has been withdrawn or superceded and should no longer be used.
